column2: SELECT TOP #  a.apogee_id,cast(str(a.glon,#,#) as float) glon,cast(str(a.glat,#,#) as float) glat,a.snr,a.vhelio_avg,a.vscatter,q.teff,q.logg,q.param_m_h,q.param_alpha_m  FROM apogeeStar as a  JOIN apogeeObject as o ON a.apogee_id=o.apogee_id  JOIN aspcapStar as q ON a.apstar_id=q.apstar_id
